{
  "stem": "4570.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were given-- they looked like ski shoes, but they were made of, of cotton or something and with a wooden sole.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a warm coat and a flannel dress with flowers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think even, even some bloomers, huge bloomers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The women who handed it out, they were the Slovaks or the Poles and they were so cruel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They never cared what they gave you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They gave the biggest woman the little garment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so sometimes we swapped things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyhow, we got this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were all dressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we stood, again, in some wide road and, and then we were put in the train and we were out of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it took-- I don't-- I can't quite remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I think it took only [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two days-- three days-- and all at once, we were in Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was called Freiberg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was near Dresden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was this enormous factory, and it was-- previously it was, I think, the biggest in Europe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A porcelain factory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that factory has been converted to make the wings of the V1 bomb.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And first we had-- we lived in the-- in the factory, which was, in a way, better because it was-- we didn't have to go outdoors.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And eventually we had-- we had to go live in some army barracks and it was very hard to-- night shift-- to walk again-- it was so cold-- to the barracks, and so we worked 12-hour shifts.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was drilling the holes for the riveting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were very small wings and we had no idea what it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "All we knew that they were only the wings, and that eventually we found out the wings have to get together with the other parts.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
